        {
            "title": "七欖︱酒吧業料生意額或增50%  帶來約2000萬元額外收益",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"七欖︱酒吧業料生意額或增50%  帶來約2000萬元額外收益\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d05975b29554875fdab3279639e9ca30/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250327/_2025032722483398479.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">七欖︱酒吧業料生意額或增50%  帶來約2000萬元額外收益</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>香港國際七人欖球賽將於明日(28日)起一連三日在啟德體育園舉行，香港酒吧業協會主席錢雋永說，預料賽事將吸引大量海外旅客來港觀賽，為酒吧業界帶來可觀收益，九龍城區的酒吧營業額有望較平日上升四至五成。\n\n</p>\n<p>他表示，今屆賽事場館可容納約五萬名觀眾，較香港大球場多出約一萬個座位，主辦方已售出超過九成門票，預計將吸引大批旅客及市民入場觀賽，帶動場館周邊酒吧的生意。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162573/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"香港酒吧業協會主席錢雋永預料賽事將吸引大量海外旅客來港觀賽，為酒吧業界帶來可觀收益。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bcb61763ecb4cf6e8f7a2969d437b554/2025-03/1256.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        香港酒吧業協會主席錢雋永預料賽事將吸引大量海外旅客來港觀賽，為酒吧業界帶來可觀收益。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>錢雋永說，球迷村提早關閉，場館設有完善交通配套接駁港島、九龍各區，方便觀眾散場後繼續消遣，有利刺激九龍及港島各區酒吧的生意，估計旺角及尖沙咀的酒吧營業額，可望上升三至四成，中環、灣仔及銅鑼灣等港島區酒吧的營業額亦預計增加兩至三成。\n\n</p>\n<p>他又說，雖然賽事尚未開始，但已有旅客觀賽前已提早「熱身」來酒吧消遣，成功帶動酒吧生意額上升，預料整個賽事期間可為香港酒吧業帶來約2000萬元的額外收益。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060667/即時-港聞-七欖︱酒吧業料生意額或增50-帶來約2000萬元額外收益",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-27 22:56:17",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "廟街動物煉獄24狗狗重拾新生 愛協：全部康復尋獲溫暖新家",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"廟街動物煉獄24狗狗重拾新生 愛協：全部康復尋獲溫暖新家\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/18b53cbf62235cead564b63c95a915f6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250327/_2025032722462981908.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">廟街動物煉獄24狗狗重拾新生 愛協：全部康復尋獲溫暖新家</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>油麻地廟街一間糧油雜貨倉庫，去年4月被揭發為動物煉獄，41隻被困貓狗飽受折磨，引起嘩然。事件至今將近一年，涉嫌殘酷對待動物父子已被判罪成，而愛護動物協會亦公布好消息，指由愛協照顧的24隻狗狗，經悉心照料後已經康復，並找到溫暖新家。\n\n</p>\n<p>事發於去年4月20日下午5時許，警方接報指一名男子在廟街踢狗，報案人其後尾隨對方至上址唐樓一單位了解。警員其後上門調查，發現單位內有合共有39隻狗同2隻貓，大部份身上沒有晶片，單位衞生極度惡劣，滿佈糞便、雜物和蟲鼠，猶如動物煉獄。事後警方拘捕單位內兩父子，涉嫌殘酷對待動物。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162561/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"愛協人員當日到場救援。愛協圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/da466822cb40490f9f64820d5553f13b/2025-03/486619801_1203142847842176_6016300074996602190_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        愛協人員當日到場救援。愛協圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162567/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"其中一狗隻懷疑戴着鴨咀式口罩太久，鼻粱有巨大傷口，經治理後已康復。愛協圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/547b6856523f162245e838736046a171/2025-03/487143207_1203142844508843_3693438709566153143_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        其中一狗隻懷疑戴着鴨咀式口罩太久，鼻粱有巨大傷口，經治理後已康復。愛協圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162566/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"愛協稱照顧的24隻狗狗已尋獲新家。愛協圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f151bc197351625f353965564693b94a/2025-03/486634000_1203142884508839_5992135422555547112_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        愛協稱照顧的24隻狗狗已尋獲新家。愛協圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162565/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7fa50c06d3a2dc3411678f778c02d9ee/2025-03/486814615_1203142841175510_6098390987919050145_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162564/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"愛協分享現時狗狗生活照，稱「全部都過得好開心」。愛協圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d889afd3758fc553d4014b6606ab0e59/2025-03/487356720_1203142867842174_8008783192509403957_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        愛協分享現時狗狗生活照，稱「全部都過得好開心」。愛協圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162563/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f533f10fe2df79c8da160f3f4415ca0a/2025-03/486727331_1203142827842178_2952312310340710074_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>愛協提到，他們收容並照顧個案中24隻狗，當時動物狀況極查，有狗隻一動不動、體重過輕或明顯患有皮膚病；亦有狗隻懷疑戴着鴨咀式口罩太久，鼻粱有巨大傷口，需接受重建手術。經照顧後，全部狗狗已逐漸康復，在警方授權下全部已找到溫暖新家。愛協又分享狗狗現時生活照，稱「全部都過得好開心」。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關報道：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/breaking-news/3337247\">廟街糧油雜貨倉變動物煉獄 父子涉虐畜被捕 逾40貓狗被困衛生情況惡劣</a></strong>\n</p>\n<p>至於涉案被捕兩父子，愛協提到兩人已承認擁有所有屋入面動物，經審訊已被判罪成，其中父親被判囚2星期、緩刑24個月；兒子則被判入獄4個月，並因公眾滋擾被罰款港幣1,000元。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162562/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"當日事件被揭發時，單位衞生及狗狗健康極度惡劣。愛協圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/60ac820a68fd1d16d94c936d2e8b26ca/2025-03/487126864_1203142894508838_5000763588694649850_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當日事件被揭發時，單位衞生及狗狗健康極度惡劣。愛協圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162560/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"愛協圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b9f7c060aef15b0c016398fd3afeb468/2025-03/487176706_1203142871175507_934772735343941153_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        愛協圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162569/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"涉事單位為廟街一糧油雜貨倉。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/25a2e2272a3566613b7dd4b6577739ed/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20240420_222051714.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉事單位為廟街一糧油雜貨倉。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162570/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b23b4bbdcc6da3d1ade841571750b7a0/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20240420_222048314.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162571/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員其後上門調查，發現單位內有合共有39隻狗同2隻貓。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0ac2fffd78977f4d343be4c60b6fc526/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20240420_222040190.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員其後上門調查，發現單位內有合共有39隻狗同2隻貓。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
